Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located in the heart of Williston, ND, this property is one block from Highway 2, the most traveled road in Williston.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
3020 1St Ave W is a large industrial warehouse located just off Highway 2 in 
Williston, ND. The property is 18,057 SF which includes 6,204 SF of office space, 11,853 SF of shop space, and two overhead cranes. The 1.43-acre parcel of land includes 26,000 SF of exterior concrete paving and the yard is fully fenced. The building features four drive-ins with large overhead doors and an extra awning for outside storage or covered parking.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Large Industrial Warehouse with Newer Office Build-Out

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: This is a great location with easy access to Highway 2, North Dakota's most East-West Highway and Highway 85 which runs North-South.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: We are pleased to offer this rare 5,000 SF industrial space for lease. The space includes approximately 550 SF of offices, a kitchenette, and restrooms including showers and laundry. There is also mezzanine space that can be used for light storage or office space if needed. The warehouse space, approximately 4,450 SF has one large overhead door, one smaller 8' x 10' door, and 3 man doors.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Four drive-ins with large overhead doors
1,200 SF office w/ two private offices
6” reinforced concrete floors with floor drains

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Adjacent to Highway 85 and just South of Highway 2, this location provides quick and easy access to all areas of the Bakken.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer for sublease this 17,500 SF industrial space in Williston, ND. This property has 400 feet of frontage along Highway 85 with heated shop space, four drive-ins, and 1,200 SF of heated and air-conditioned office space with mezzanine above.    
The property is zoned industrial and can be leased as a 7,500 SF suite, 10,000 SF suite, or a 17,500 SF suite. There is a demising wall in-place between the 7,500 SF shop and the 10,000 SF shop/office.  The three-acre parcel of land has 59,000 SF of exterior concrete paving and is easily accessible from two major traffic routes. The building totals 25,000 SF and is currently a multi-tenant building.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Fenced yard w/ 28,000 SF concrete apron
13 total drive-ins with large overhead doors
6" reinforced concrete floors w/ floor drains

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located along Highway 85 just South of the intersection of Highway 85 and Highway 2, this location provides great access to all areas of the Bakken.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer this 19,420 SF industrial property in Williston, ND for sublease. This property has 300 feet of frontage along Highway 85 and consists of two industrial buildings with heated shop space, 6” reinforced concrete floors and 3,276 SF of office space. Building 100 is 10,000 SF with 2,296 SF of office space with mezzanine above and Building 200 is 9,420 SF with 980 SF of office space. 
The 10,000 SF building has four drive-ins with 18’-wide by 17’-high overhead doors and was built in 2008.  The 9,420 SF building has nine drive-ins with 12’-wide by 14’-high overhead doors and was built in 2010.  The yard is fully fenced with a gate entry and there is a 28,000 SF concrete apron and 8,500 SF of asphalt parking.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: This property is located along Highway 85 just south of the intersection of Highway 85 and Highway 2, providing great access to all areas of the Bakken.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE is pleased to offer this 11,250 SF industrial shop for sublease in Williston, ND. The property features four drive-ins and sits on 2.3 acres of land with a fenced yard. The current Tenant's lease term expires October 31, 2022 and the building is available immediately.
